entries.femaleVariant: Tygers're comin' today. For the rent. Just got a message.
Had a bad week... First my kid's sick, then that firefight scared people off...
Maybe they'll let it go? I always pay on time. Anyone can slip up once, right?
Listen to me. Get the eds. Now. Dunno how, maybe you gotta yank out some implants, sell a kidney. Otherwise, they'll take it out on all of us! Got it?
